list.name: Deploys
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
   time_sec,
   description as text,
   tags
  FROM event
  WHERE $__unixEpochFilter(time_sec) AND tags='deploy'
  ORDER BY 1 ASC

list.name: Tickets
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
   time_sec as time,
   description as text,
   tags
  FROM event
  WHERE $__unixEpochFilter(time_sec) AND tags='ticket'
  ORDER BY 1 ASC

list.name: Metric Values timeEpoch macro
list.rawQuery:
SELECT 
  $__timeEpoch(time), 
  measurement as text, 
  '' as tags
FROM
  metric_values 
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY 1

list.name: Metric Values native time
list.rawQuery:
SELECT 
  time, 
  measurement as text, 
  '' as tags
FROM
  metric_values 
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY 1

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  $__timeGroup(time, '$summarize') as time, 
  CONCAT(measurement, ' - value one') as metric, 
  avg(valueOne) as valueOne
FROM
  metric_values 
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND
  measurement IN($metric)
GROUP BY 1, 2
ORDER BY 1

SELECT 
  $__timeGroup(time, '$summarize') as time, 
  CONCAT(measurement, ' - value two') as metric, 
  avg(valueTwo) as valueTwo 
FROM
  metric_values
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND
  measurement IN($metric)
GROUP BY 1,2
ORDER BY 1
